asset.hookText:
Are you ready to GET REAL about your sport performance underwear? Get Jockey Sport. We've spent over a century perfecting what we do best -- underwear. From real athletes like Babe Ruth to real, everyday athletes like you, Jockey delivers the innovation athletes need to perform at their peak.

Our new Jockey Sport underwear is built with every feature a real, #EverydayAthlete needs: odor control, cooling, quick-drying. To prove it, we tested Jockey Sport at a world-renowned biomechanics lab, on real athletes, analyzing speed, range of motion, agility and power. What did we find out? 

No other underwear tested fights odor better or dries faster to keep you cooler. http://bit.ly/10sBlkk
